sentence: In trading on Wednesday, the iShares North American Tech-Software ETF is outperforming other ETFs, up about 3.6% on the day.
Components of that ETF showing particular strength include shares of Zendesk, up about 8.2% and shares of SALESFORCE.COM, up about 8.1% on the day.
And underperforming other ETFs today is the First Trust Preferred Securities and Income ETF, off about 0.3% in Wednesday afternoon trading.
